In preparation for Outlander we re taking the STARZ App to the next level. With this update you ll have a faster download and load time an improved homescreen experience better navigation easier login and improved profiles. Be on the lookout for the next release during the mid season of Outlander for more improvements based on your feedback. And don t forget to check out the Outlander Behind the Scenes bonus videos!

The STARZ app is here. We ve merged STARZ Play ENCORE Play and MOVIEPLEX Play to deliver the best entertainment all in one place. A new design and added functionality lets you download your shows and movies to watch whenever wherever. STARZ Stream it. Download it. Watch it. Update now.

STARZ Play users we hear you! The video playback error resulting in a black screen is a thing of the past. Update now to get the best viewing experience.
Play List is here! Add movies or original series to your Play List to watch later. Play List will also allow you to easily continue watching right where you left off. Update now to get it!
